WHY AGPL?

I built Code Sergeant to help people with ADHD and focus challenges - people
like me. This license ensures the project stays open and benefits the community.
If you build something commercial with this code, you're required to share your
improvements back, which helps everyone.

For questions about licensing or commercial partnerships, reach out:
ceo@cuevalabs.com

